              <a name="TeamFoundationSidekicks"></a><h2>Team Foundation Sidekicks 2010</h2>
              <p>Team Foundation Sidekicks is a great tool that gives you additional information about your TFS projects.  It’s a must-have for your TFS Master to help make sure the <a href="http://rules.ssw.com.au/TFS/RulesToBetterVersionControlwithTFS(AKASourceControl)/Pages/default.aspx">Rules to Better Version Control with TFS</a> are being followed.</p>
              <ol>
                Some of the great things it can tell you include:
