               <li>Whether a developer has files checked out on multiple workspaces – see <a href="http://rules.ssw.com.au/TFS/RulesToBetterVersionControlwithTFS(AKASourceControl)/Pages/DeleteWorkspaces.aspx">Do you know to delete workspaces older than 6 months and warn on 3?</a></li>
